          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By authors. Available experimental values are",
                "normalized to these predictions by setting the sum of",
                "the corresponding theoretical cross sections. The",
                "separation efficiencies for different isotopes of a",
                "given element are assumed to be equal. One can see that",
                "the neutron-rich slopes of experimental isotopes",
                "distributions are described quite well. Although, no",
                "experimentally observed odd-even fluctuations are",
                "reproduced."
